{"tid":1978234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日全國進入緊急狀態","createTime":"2020-04-18T14:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T16:44:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b849aceaedcbbc35e4068d1cbbe39525d9ef8689","tid":1978234,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200417/CTXWEV2V54SNTZNBFZTT2QRI24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2FCTXWEV2V54SNTZNBFZTT2QRI24%2F&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=f9bc5c00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2FCTXWEV2V54SNTZNBFZTT2QRI24%2F&h=ce7cf7b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200417/CTXWEV2V54SNTZNBFZTT2QRI24/</a><br />\n<br />\n日全國進入緊急狀態<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200417/large/1587053354_7f88.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200417%2Flarge%2F1587053354_7f88.gif&h=3cdbcf38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東京一個戶外吸煙區被封，避免民眾聚集。 路透社<br />\n<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三昨日宣佈，將全國納入「緊急事態宣言」，由原本的七都府縣擴大至全國47都道府縣，至5月6日為止。<br />\n<br />\n安倍晉三政府昨日跟專家委員會開會後召開記者會，宣佈「緊急事態宣言」擴至全國，其中特別提到北海道、茨城縣、石川縣、岐阜縣、愛知縣和京都縣的疫情，已擴大至跟之前納入「緊急事態宣言」的七個道府縣相若。至於其他府縣，亦因為人流活動或令疫情擴散，故此宣佈全國進入「緊急事態」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安倍妻再被揭群聚<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：居港德籍夫婦創辦<br />\n<br />\n日本政府於上周二首度實施「緊急事態宣言」，呼籲民眾留在家中而未有具體強制性措施或罰則，數個未被納入的地區自行宣佈沒有法律約束力的「緊急事態」。日本至昨日累計得9,228宗確診個案、186人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n而第一夫人安倍昭惠繼上次被攝得與朋友聚餐賞櫻後，再被揭上月中曾與50人到神社參拜，激起網民眾怒，質疑她如因此染疫會否得到醫院特別待遇。<br />\n<br />\n兩個醫療組織表示「感覺到醫療系統即將崩潰」，指醫院將無法接收非武肺的輕症患者。不過東京都內已有多間醫院擔心院內感染而拒絕接收疑似患者。一名年逾80的男子上周五出現食慾不振及脫水等症狀後，乘救護車入院，當時未有發燒，院方檢查發現他肺部有疑似陰影，懷疑他患武肺，為他轉介到其他醫院接受治療，但遭約110間醫療機構拒收，至有醫院接收已耗費10小時。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"a2a652af013a0656d4a876c901a85dfc3c2c54f9","tid":1978234,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">英國查黑警違反人權 最後2日deadline</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1978200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1978200</a>"},{"pid":"4515b7c66337aa6172ae0e39be64d8cbcd5b0eac","tid":1978234,"uid":268519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4DD6Q07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4DD6Q07.jpg&h=9ea5fe5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"373f7c76f02c1f6e50c41f6e6cc4b1a52606e781","tid":1978234,"uid":196535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"希望日本捱得過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bc5d00f1541611d151dcfe98e49a3722b0f3d7","tid":1978234,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166d37c2054e0b4bf69245b407448910f57915d8","tid":1978234,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線好需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nTwitter文宣組<br />\n戰線台 @twittermansyunzou <br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線 @reddithk_channel<br />\n文宣 @hkstandstrong